The '''''Rusted Cutlass''''' was a an old battered [[Corvette/Legends|corvette]] owned by the [[Dread Pirate]] [[Mendel Cutter]]. When Cutter decided to retire from piracy, he attached his ship to [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

When ''Zirtran's Anchor'' reappeared after its mysterious disappearance, the ''Rusted Cutlass'' was missing, leading people to think that Cutter actually escaped the disaster.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

[[Leo Bellsfar/Legends|Leo Bellsfar]] of the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]] named [[Rusted Cutlass II|his ship]] after the ''Rusted Cutlass''.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

